盘疯狂写入\r\n\r\n重启（勾选重新打开所有 app ）之后 swap 就降下来了，磁盘也不疯狂写入了\r\n\r\niCloud 同步也是，重启之后疯狂同步，因为重启之前 iCloud 实际上没同步好，发生了故障\r\n\r\nmacOS 的 bug 真多啊","content_rendered":"<p>感觉 macOS 的内存管理依托答辩一样，用久了就会狂写 ssd 。比如我 16G RAM ，开软件多了，swap 到 10 个 G 。这时候我把耗内存多的软件都退出了，swap 还是 10 个 G ，而且磁盘疯狂写入</p>\n<p>重启（勾选重新打开所有 app ）之后 swap 就降下来了，磁盘也不疯狂写入了</p>\n<p>iCloud 同步也是，重启之后疯狂同步，因为重启之前 iCloud 实际上没同步好，发生了故障</p>\n<p>macOS 的 bug 真多啊</p>\n","last_modified":1679622646,"replies":103,"id":926735},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":54559,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181","stars":8292,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":505801,"username":"nunterr","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/nunterr","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f1587c764c2ba142b1955f4ac9968df5?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f1587c764c2ba142b1955f4ac9968df5?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f1587c764c2ba142b1955f4ac9968df5?s=73&d=retro","created":1598606121,"last_modified":1673255330},"last_reply_by":"wolfie","last_touched":1679646073,"title":"自从我用了小米 11 pro 之后，我 10 年的米粉生涯彻底结束，以后再也不会买小米手机","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/926773","created":1679627080,"deleted":0,"content":"自从我用了小米 11 pro 之后，我 10 年的米粉生涯彻底结束，以后再也不会买小米手机，立帖为证","content_rendered":"自从我用了小米 11 pro 之后，我 10 年的米粉生涯彻底结束，以后再也不会买小米手机，立帖为证","last_modified":1679627080,"replies":84,"id":926773},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181","name":"programmer","a